<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edeg">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        #con{
            width:700px;
            height: 500px;
            margin: 0px auto;

            background-image: linear-gradient(45deg,#CCFBFF,#EF96C5,#EAD6EE,#A0F1EA,#EEBD89,#D13ABD,#F9957F,#F2F5D0);
            
            position: relative;
        }
        h1{
            text-align: center;
            height: 100px;
            line-height: 100px;
        }
        #con>div{
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            border: 1px solid #D13ABD;
            border-radius: 50%;
            text-align: center;

            background-color: #F9957F;

            position: absolute;

            transition: transform 1s;
        }
        .card1{
            left: 30px;
            top: 70px;
            transform:rotate(30deg);
        }
        .card2{
            left: 130px ;
            top: 230px;
            transform:rotate(-30deg);
        }
        .card3{
            left: 450px;
            top: 280px;
            transform:rotate(45deg);
        }
        .card4{
            left: 460px;
            top: 100px;
            transform:rotate(180deg);
        }
        p{
            text-indent: 2em;
        }
        #con>div:hover{
			z-indenx:9;
            transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1.3,1.3);
        }
    </style>
</head>
    
<body>
    <div id="con">
        <h1>Happy Wall</h1>
        <div class="card1">
            <h4>祝福小王</h4>
            <p>我来自偶然像一颗尘土有谁看出我的脆弱我来自何方我情归何处谁在下一刻呼唤我</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card2">
            <h4>祝福小浩</h4>
            <p>天地虽宽这条路却难走我看遍这人间坎坷辛苦我还有多少爱我还有多少泪要苍天知道我不认输</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card3">
            <h4>祝福小成</h4>
            <p>感恩的心感谢有你
                伴我一生
                让我有勇气做我自己
                感恩的心感谢命运
                花开花落
                我一样会珍惜
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card4">
            <h4>祝福小八</h4>
            <p>我来自偶然像一颗尘土有谁看出我的脆弱</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>